Node "David_1c_1"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "I want to thank you for helping to convince Alexander to ban euthanasia in Sandover. I wish I'd thought of trying to bring Catherine onside. I guess she's a lot more grown up than I'd assumed."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Don't mention it. I need to ask you a question, though." linkto "David_1c_2"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Sorry, I thought you were someone else. It's the robes. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "David_1c_2"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Naturally, it'd be my pleasure. What do you need to know?"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "What do you do around here?" linkto "David_1a_3" conditions { LOCAL_VARIABLE  == 0 link_next  } notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "What do you and Michael do in Sandover?" linkto "David_2c_1" conditions { LOCAL_VARIABLE  > 0 link_next NONE } notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "What made you decide to become Michael's assistant?" linkto "David_3_1" conditions { LOCAL_VARIABLE  > 0 link_next  } notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Actually, I don't think I need to ask you anything. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "David_1d_1"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "I hope you're happy with yourself. Now that Alexander has officially made euthanasia legal in Sandover, the flood-gates are open for mass slaughter. You've no idea what you've done."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "If you'd look past your own prejudices, you'd see that it's for the best." linkto "David_1d_2B_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I'm sorry you feel that way." linkto "David_1d_2a_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Get over it. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "David_1d_2a_1"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Well, what's done is done. I've never had my faith in human nature more sorely tested though, let me tell you that."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Can I ask you a question?" linkto "David_1d_2a_2"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "If you'd look past your own prejudices, you'd see that it's for the best." linkto "David_1d_2B_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Get over it. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
