          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "What made you decide to become Michael's assistant?" linkto "David_3_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Thanks. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "David_2c_1"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "The people of Sandover call Michael their priest, mostly because he and I take care of the sort of roles and jobs that priests do."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "What religion do you follow?" linkto "David_2c_2a"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "What roles and jobs are those?" linkto "David_2c_2b"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "What made you decide to become Michael's assistant?" linkto "David_3_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I have to go. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "David_2c_2a"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "There's no single, major religion in Sandover. People just worship God, or whatever you want to call him, in their own way."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "So what do you both actually do?" linkto "David_2c_2b"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "What made you decide to become Michael's assistant?" linkto "David_3_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I have to go. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "David_2c_2b"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "You should talk to Michael about that. He's been looking after the Sandover flock much longer than me."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "What religion do you follow?" linkto "David_2c_2a"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "What made you decide to become Michael's assistant?" linkto "David_3_1"  notes ""
