Node "David_3_1"
notes "The David_3_* path is where the PC can find out that David is strongly opposed to euthanasia."
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "I would have volunteered to take up a position like Michael's if he hadn't already been here. I like to be active helping people. I'm a pretty morally-guided sort of guy."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Does it make you jealous that people look to Michael as their priest, rather than you?" linkto "David_3_2a"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "You do-gooder types sicken me." linkto "David_3_2B"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Tell me more about the morals that guide you." linkto "David_3_2c_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Can I ask you about something else, instead?" linkto "David_9"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I have to go. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "David_3_2a"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "I find it strange that you'd even ask. Absolutely not. I'm just glad there are two of us that are doing this."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "You do-gooder types sicken me." linkto "David_3_2B"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Tell me more about the morals that guide you." linkto "David_3_2c_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Can I ask you about something else, instead?" linkto "David_9"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I have to go. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "David_3_2B"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "[He seems unfazed.] Funny how many people feel threatened by someone who just wants to make the world a better place."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Does it make you jealous that people look to Michael as their priest, rather than you?" linkto "David_3_2a"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Tell me more about the morals that guide you." linkto "David_3_2c_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Can I ask you about something else, instead?" linkto "David_9"  notes ""
