is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Hallelujah! I knew you were the compassionate sort. Listen, get out there and spread the word. Be active. *Tell* people that what's going on here, in our homes, is wrong."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "How will I convince them?" linkto "David_3_4_3b_2"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Can I ask you about something else, instead?" linkto "David_9"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I have to go. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "David_3_4_3b_2"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Let me give you some of the strongest arguments against euthanasia. The more people Sandover's residents hear them from, the more likely they are to pay attention to them."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Okay, I'm all ears." linkto "David_4_1_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Can I ask you about something else, instead?" linkto "David_9"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I have to go. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "David_4_1_1"
notes "The David 4_* path is where the PC can listen to David's anti-euthanasia arguments."
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Okay, well, think about this: a lot of people think that there are only two alternatives open to patients with a terminal illness. On the one hand, they die slowly in painful, unrelieved suffering; on the other hand, they receive euthanasia. With me so far?"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "With you." linkto "David_4_1_2"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I have to go. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "David_4_1_2"
notes "Thus ends the first lesson. Increment the variable David_Euth_Arg_1 by 1."
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "There is, however, another, third way - compassionate medical care. You can use drugs to alleviate the pain of, if not to cure, a terminal illness. That's what medicine is supposed to be about, after all."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Is Sandover able to afford the sort of drugs regimens you're describing, though?" linkto "David_4_1_3a" conditions { CHECK_STAT perception > 5 link_next AND, CHECK_STAT intelligence > 5 link_next NONE } notes "Note mild INT and PER checks. INT to think of the counter-argument and PER to notice that Sandover is a poverty-stricken dump."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I see." linkto "David_4_1_3b "  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I have to go. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "David_4_1_3a"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "[You notice a slight flicker of irritation on his face.] Not at the moment, maybe. That doesn't mean there are plenty more reasons not to just go round slaughtering ill Sandover people, though."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Let's hear your next reason." linkto "David_4_2_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Let me ask you about something else instead." linkto "David_9"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I have to go. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "David_4_1_3b "
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "That's the first reason and that's just for starters. Let me tell you a few of the others."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Sure." linkto "David_4_2_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Let me ask you about something else instead." linkto "David_9"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I have to go. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "David_4_2_1"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Why do people become doctors in the first place? To help other people get better, am I right?"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Right." linkto "David_4_2_2"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL Gender=MALE playertext "I always thought it was to impress chicks, but I guess so." linkto "David_4_2_2"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I have to go. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "David_4_2_2"
notes "Thus ends the second lesson. Increment the variable David_Euth_Arg_2 by 1."
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "If we ask our doctors to kill their own patients, that's going to put them off learning medicine in the first place. Who actually *wants* that kind of ethical burden? Mark my words: you legalize euthanasia, you say goodbye to dedicated health-workers."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I've never thought about that before." linkto "David_4_2_3"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I've heard that line of reasoning before." linkto "David_4_2_3"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I have to go. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "David_4_2_3"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "In that case, let me give you another line of reasoning."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Please do." linkto "David_4_3_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Let me ask you about something else instead." linkto "David_9"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I have to go. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "David_4_3_1"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "When considerate people are dying, the last thing they want is to be a burden to anybody. They have no desire to be selfish, or to even appear to be selfish."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Go on." linkto "David_4_3_2a_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I think I can see where you're going with this." linkto "David_4_3_2a_1" conditions { CHECK_STAT intelligence > 5 link_next NONE } notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "The last person I saw die was more concerned with wanting me not to kill him." linkto "David_4_3_2b"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I have to go. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "David_4_3_2a_1"
notes "Thus ends the third lesson. Increment the variable David_Euth_Arg_3 by 1."
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "I know for a fact that some very ill people feel that assisted suicide is something they *ought* to request, as a matter of duty, for the sake of their families and the overstretched healthcare facilities in Sandover."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Have you spoken to any of these very ill people yourself?" linkto "David_4_3_2a_2a"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I suppose you're right." linkto "David_4_3_2a_2b"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I have to go. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "David_4_3_2a_2a"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "'Spoken' to them? Some of them were friends of mine! That's why we have to make sure that Sandover pressures its leaders into banning the practise as soon as possible."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Let me hear the next reason against euthanasia." linkto "David_4_4_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Let me ask you about something else instead." linkto "David_9"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I have to go. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "David_4_3_2a_2b"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "There's no 'suppose' about it. I've lost good friends of mine because they felt guilty just for living."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Let me hear the next reason against euthanasia." linkto "David_0"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Let me ask you about something else instead." linkto "David_9"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I have to go. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
