Node "David_4_4_1"
notes "Thus ends the fourth lesson. Increment the variable David_Euth_Arg_4 by 1."
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "The next one's fairly simple. Doctors make mistakes. What if Dr. Oswald is wrong when he says a patient has no chances of survival, and that patient then asks to be euthanased as a result? He or she dies unnecessarily."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Do you think Dr. Oswald makes many mistakes?" linkto "David_4_4_2"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I have to go. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "David_4_4_2"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Well, I'm not a doctor, so who knows, other than he himself? One thing's for sure: I don't know of any great medical schools in the wastes, so it's not hard to imagine how limited his skills are."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Do you think Dr. Oswald should not be practising medicine at all?" linkto "David_4_4_3a"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "What other reasons do you have against the use of euthanasia?" linkto "David_4_4_3b"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Let me ask you a question about something else." linkto "David_9"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I have to go. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "David_4_4_3a"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Hey, don't get me wrong. He's the most skilled person in Sandover when it comes to medical matters. He shouldn't be in a position to take lives, though. Not that anyone should."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "What other reasons do you have against the use of euthanasia?" linkto "David_4_4_3b"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Let me ask you a question about something else." linkto "David_9"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I have to go. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "David_4_4_3b"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Just one more. You're a good listener. [He smiles.]"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Let's hear it." linkto "David_4_5_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I have to go. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Let me ask you a question about something else." linkto "David_9"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "David_4_5_1"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Last but not least: most of the people I've spoken to who are in favor of euthanasia think it should only be used in cases where the patient has no hope of survival, and when they're suffering badly."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Sounds like a reasonable view point." linkto "David_4_5_2"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Go on." linkto "David_4_5_2"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I have to go. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "David_4_5_2"
notes "Thus ends the fifth and final lesson. Increment the variable David_Euth_Arg_5 by 1."
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "But when we give people the freedom to ask, well, maybe even demand, to die, where does it end? Today, euthanasia for those with terminal cancer; what comes tomorrow - euthanasia for those with depression?"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I see what you mean." linkto "David_4_5_3"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Let me ask you about something else." linkto "David_9"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I have to go. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "David_4_5_3"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Those are my five most powerful arguments I use to oppose euthanasia. There are more, but if those five don't do it, there's usually not much point going on."
      options {
